NAME

    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::MojibakeTests - Author tests for source encoding

VERSION

    version 0.8

SYNOPSIS

    In dist.ini:

        [MojibakeTests]

DESCRIPTION

    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following file:

        xt/author/mojibake.t - a standard Test::Mojibake test

AUTHOR

    Stanislaw Pusep <stas@sysd.org>

